    "By addressing these concerns, LLM can be effectively integrated as a valuable tool to augment clinical decision-making, improve patient care, and advance the field of diagnostic medicine [2,3,5,11,15,16].To harness the potential of LLMs, a collaborative and iterative approach is necessary.",
